00:01:45.806 --> 00:01:51.546
Brian Samuel Epstein was born in 1934, the first-born son of a

00:01:51.566 --> 00:01:56.056
middle-class Jewish family in Liverpool, in the north-west of England.

00:01:57.066 --> 00:02:00.996
Epstein had a relatively privileged childhood, attending

00:02:01.236 --> 00:02:04.776
